@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName "Noto Sans CJK SC"
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
left to right direction

actor "API 调用方\n(业务系统/脚本)" as ApiCaller
actor "SIP 客户端\n(MicroSIP/Sipnetic)" as SipClient

node "Control Plane\nNode.js" as Control {
  component "Express API\n(src/app.js)" as Api
  component "CallService\n(src/services/call-service.js)" as CallSvc
  component "CallStateMachine\n(src/services/call-state-machine.js)" as SM
  component "AmiClient\n(src/asterisk/ami-client.js)" as Ami
  component "SystemServiceManager\n(src/services/system-service-manager.js)" as OpsSvc
  component "Dashboard\n(src/web/*)" as Dashboard
}

database "SQLite\n(data/privacy.db)" as DB
node "Asterisk\nPJSIP + Dialplan" as Ast
cloud "PSTN / SIP Trunk\n(可选)" as Trunk

ApiCaller --> Api : HTTP /v1/*\n(x-api-key)
SipClient --> Ast : SIP INVITE / REGISTER

Api --> CallSvc : createCall/getCall
Api --> OpsSvc : /v1/ops/*
Api --> Dashboard : /dashboard 静态资源

CallSvc --> DB : 读写 calls/users/virtual_numbers
CallSvc --> Ami : AMI Originate
Ami --> Ast : TCP 5038
Ast --> Ami : AMI Events\n(OriginateResponse/UserEvent/Hangup)
Ami --> SM : event
SM --> DB : 状态回写\n(calls/call_legs)

Ast --> Trunk : B-leg 外呼(可选)
Ast --> SipClient : 本地 endpoint 呼叫

Dashboard --> Api : /v1/ops/overview
Dashboard --> Api : /v1/ops/services/*

@enduml
